trans-unit.source: Controls the strictness of the code generated by the common language runtime's just-in-time (JIT) compiler.
trans-unit.target: Controla a limitação do código gerado pelo compilador Just-In-Time (JIT) do Common Language Runtime.

trans-unit.source: Apply the <xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxationsAttribute> attribute to assemblies to specify assembly compilation parameters.
trans-unit.target: Aplicar o <xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxationsAttribute> de atributo para assemblies para especificar parâmetros de compilação do assembly.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxations> enumeration to specify compilation options.
trans-unit.target: Use o <xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxations> enumeração para especificar opções de compilação.

trans-unit.source: This attribute is ignored in version 1.0 of the Microsoft .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: Esse atributo é ignorado na versão 1.0 do Microsoft .NET Framework.

trans-unit.source: The classes in <xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices> are for compiler writers' use only.
trans-unit.target: As classes em <xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices> são autores de compilador apenas para uso.

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates how to apply the <xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxationsAttribute>.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo a seguir demonstra como aplicar o <xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxationsAttribute>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxationsAttribute" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxationsAttribute" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxationsAttribute" /> class with the specified compilation relaxations.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxationsAttribute" /> com as reduções de compilação especificadas.

trans-unit.source: Apply the <xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxationsAttribute> attribute to assemblies to specify assembly compilation parameters.
trans-unit.target: Aplicar o <xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxationsAttribute> de atributo para assemblies para especificar parâmetros de compilação do assembly.

trans-unit.source: This attribute is ignored in version 1.0 of the Microsoft .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: Esse atributo é ignorado na versão 1.0 do Microsoft .NET Framework.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxationsAttribute" /> class with the specified <see cref="T:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxations" /> value.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxationsAttribute" /> com o valor <see cref="T:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxations" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: Apply the <xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxationsAttribute> attribute to assemblies to specify assembly compilation parameters.
trans-unit.target: Aplicar o <xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxationsAttribute> de atributo para assemblies para especificar parâmetros de compilação do assembly.

trans-unit.source: This attribute is ignored in version 1.0 of the Microsoft .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: Esse atributo é ignorado na versão 1.0 do Microsoft .NET Framework.

trans-unit.source: Gets the compilation relaxations specified when the current object was constructed.
trans-unit.target: Obtém as reduções de compilação especificadas quando o objeto atual foi construído.

trans-unit.source: The compilation relaxations specified when the current object was constructed.
trans-unit.target: As reduções de compilação especificada quando o objeto atual foi construído.

trans-unit.source: Use the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxations" /> enumeration with the <see cref="P:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxationsAttribute.CompilationRelaxations" /> property.
trans-unit.target: Use o <see cref="T:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxations" /> enumeração com o <see cref="P:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.CompilationRelaxationsAttribute.CompilationRelaxations" /> propriedade.
